         >> metis_tac [IN_COUNT])
   >- metis_tac [mem_alphabet]
   >- (`normalize r IN fdom regexp_compare (singleton (normalize r) 0)`
          by (rw [fdom_def, singleton_def,lookup_def,EQ_IMP_THM]
